N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 21 ยง 9700.8 - Fees

State Regulations
(a) The fee for
photocopies not exceeding 9 x 14 inches is 25 cents per page. (b) The fee for copies of records other than
photocopies which are 9 x 14 inches or less in size shall be the actual copying
cost excluding fixed agency costs such as salaries. Notes
